Flex Runner Sun PS 'Wings Swoosh'
results.story: Crafted for little kids, the Nike Flex Runner Sun PS ‘Wings Swoosh’ uses dynamic colors and refreshed branding to express a feeling of free movement. A winged Nike Swoosh adorns a synthetic leather overlay in a gradient pink and yellow finish, contrasted by a mesh and textile build in Platinum Tint. The slip-on silhouette, equipped with prominent pull tabs for easy on and off, rides on a soft foam sole unit in pristine Summit White.

results.name: Flex Runner PS 'Laser Blue Crimson'
results.story: Built for little kids, the Nike Flex Runner PS ‘Laser Blue Crimson’ highlights bright colors on a versatile slip-on silhouette. An electric blue finish is applied to the stretchy textile upper, equipped with vibrant orange pull tabs that deliver easy on and off. A midfoot overlay constructed from black synthetic leather provides structural support and added durability. The eye-catching composition up top is supported by a stark white foam sole unit, offering lightweight cushioning with each step.

results.name: Scramjet 3 PS 'Laser Green'
results.story: Constructed for little kids, the Under Armour Scramjet 3 PS ‘Laser Green’ highlights vivid accents on a running shoe inspired by jets. Stretch bungee laces secure a mesh upper fortified with seamless synthetic overlays and a rigid external heel counter. A plush sockliner acts in tandem with a full-length EVA midsole to provide lightweight cushioning with each step. Underfoot, rubber pods are placed in high-wear areas for improved durability and traction.

results.name: Scramjet 3 PS 'Beta Yellow Ray'
results.story: Crafted for toddlers, the Scramjet 3 PS ‘Beta Yellow Ray’ highlights bold hues on a lightweight running shoe inspired by jets. Elastic bungee laces secure a crimson mesh upper reinforced with synthetic no-sew overlays. Neon yellow accents land on the sneaker’s branding elements and EVA midsole, its cushioning capabilities enhanced with a plush sockliner. Strategically placed rubber pods under the heel and forefoot deliver enhanced durability and traction.

results.name: Flex Runner PS 'Active Fuchsia'
results.story: Featuring a convenient slip-on build for little kids, the Nike Flex Runner PS ‘Active Fuchsia’ shows off a candy-bright hue on the stretchy textile upper. Webbing pull tabs at the tongue and heel provide easy on and off, while a synthetic leather midfoot cage delivers structural support and added durability. The lightweight sneaker rides on a soft foam sole unit, featuring multiple flex grooves that promote the natural movement of the foot.

results.name: Roshe Golf GS 'Infrared'
results.story: Made for big kids, the Nike Roshe Golf GS ‘Infrared’ brings the minimalist comfort of the original Roshe to the fairway. Neutral grey tones are applied to the breathable mesh upper, equipped with a gusseted tongue and accented with vibrant pops of Infrared on the rear pull tab and external heel counter. The lightweight build rides on an injected foam midsole, supported by a pressure-mapped outsole that provides grippy traction in key zones.

results.name: Scramjet 3 PS 'Vibe Orange'
results.story: Developed for pre-schoolers, the Under Armour Scramjet 3 PS ‘Vibe Orange’ showcases sharply contrasting hues that accentuate the sneaker’s dynamic lines. Varying shades of orange are applied to the mesh upper, accented with royal blue branding hits and reinforced with seamless overlays. An external heel counter provides enhanced stability, while the one-piece EVA midsole packs abundant foam for plush cushioning and a smooth ride.

results.name: Roshe Golf GS 'Pure Platinum Black'
results.story: Crafted for big kids, the Nike Roshe Golf GS ‘Pure Platinum Black’ applies a two-tone color scheme to a course-ready version of the minimalist Roshe silhouette. Updated details include a rigid heel counter, a gusseted tongue, and a thin film over the mesh upper for added protection against water and debris. The sneaker’s tooling features a cupsole-like design, highlighted by a lightweight injected foam midsole and pressure-mapped integrated-traction outsole.

results.name: Roshe Golf GS 'White Black'
results.story: Built for big kids, the Nike Roshe Golf GS ‘White Black’ replicates the look of the original Roshe, highlighted by neutral tones on a minimalist mesh upper. Upgraded details include an external heel counter for improved rearfoot stability and a gusseted tongue designed to keep debris out. Lightweight cushioning arrives via an injected foam midsole. Underfoot, an integrated traction pattern on the pressure-mapped outsole provides optimal grip during rotational movements.

results.name: Duramo SL J 'Black Camo'
results.story: Offered in grade school sizing, the adidas Duramo SL J ‘Black Camo’ combines traditional laces with an adjustable hook and loop strap to secure the breathable mesh upper. Shiny metallic silver three-stripes and a camo-print heel panel bring added style to the otherwise monochrome design. The versatile sneaker is mounted on a soft Cloudfoam midsole, good for plush cushioning with each step. A durable full-length rubber outsole provides grippy traction underfoot.

Embiid One GS 'Draft Night'
results.story: Built for big kids, the Under Armour Embiid One GS ‘Draft Night’ dresses Joel Embiid’s debut signature shoe with a breathable white mesh upper. Vibrant accents are added to the sneaker’s supportive TPU wings and Micro G foam midsole, reflecting the colors seen on a ‘Please Stand By’ broadcast screen — a nod to the viral moment of the 2014 NBA Draft, when an untimely tape delay appeared to capture Embiid’s utterly emotionless reaction to being selected by the Philadelphia 76ers with the third overall pick.

Yeezy Boost 380 Kids 'Hylte'
results.story: The adidas Yeezy Boost 380 Kids ‘Hylte’ delivers an eye-catching colorway of the minimalist slip-on silhouette. The re-engineered Primeknit upper is rendered in a mix of mustard yellow and honeyed tan hues, while the translucent monofilament window is distinguished by an eye-catching neon green finish. Lightweight cushioning comes courtesy of a full-length Boost midsole, wrapped in a grey rubber cage and supported by a herringbone rubber outsole. The Yeezy Boost 380 Kids 'Hylte’ is a regional exclusive and only launched in North America and Latin America.

NASA x ZX 2K J 'Cloud Silver Metallic'
results.story: Made for big kids, the NASA x adidas ZX 2K J ‘Cloud Silver Metallic’ leverages sharply contrasting hues to accentuate the sneaker’s Boost midsole, partially wrapped in semi-transparent TPU and finished in a gradient blend of fluorescent orange and metallic silver. Up top, breathable white textile is accented with metallic silver three-stripes and royal blue detailing on the toe box. A matching blue pull tab at the heel provides easy on and off.

results.name: NASA x ZX 2K Little Kid 'Cloud Silver Metallic'
results.story: Launching as part of a larger collection developed in partnership with the American space agency, the NASA x adidas ZX 2K Little Kid ‘Cloud Silver Metallic’ adds vibrant accents to a lifestyle runner built for comfort. The sneaker utilizes a breathable textile upper accented with metallic silver three-stripes and Artemis tongue tags, the latter celebrating NASA’s lunar mission program. Lightweight cushioning arrives via a partially caged EVA midsole, finished in a gradient blend orange and metallic silver.

results.name: NASA x ZX 2K J 'Dash Grey Silver'
results.story: Constructed for big kids, the NASA x adidas ZX 2K J ‘Dash Grey Silver’ dresses the lifestyle runner in lightweight textile, its pale grey finish enlivened by contrasting neon pops of color and metallic silver three-stripes. NASA branding adorns the sockliner, while Artemis badges give a nod to the American space agency’s mission to return astronauts to the moon by 2024. A color-fade effect in black and metallic silver is applied to the Boost midsole, partially caged in semi-translucent TPU that wraps around the heel.

results.name: NASA x ZX 2K Little Kid 'Dash Grey Silver'
results.story: The NASA x adidas ZX 2K Little Kid ‘Dash Grey Silver’ delivers a lightweight runner for a new generation of space enthusiasts. The light grey textile upper is accented with metallic silver three-stripes and Artemis badges atop the tongue — a nod to NASA’s lunar mission program. The sneaker’s space travel theme comes into sharper focus on the full-length Boost midsole, finished in a gradient blend of silver and black, the latter hue contrasted by white speckles to mimic the vast expanse of outer space.

The rest of the upper is crafted from breathable mesh in a slate blue finish, enlivened by a series of neon no-sew overlays on the forefoot and eyestay.

Air Max 90 PS 'Christmas Sweater'
results.story: Built for little kids, the Nike Air Max 90 PS ‘Christmas Sweater’ features a festive design that captures the holiday spirit. An all-over snowflake print in Lucky Green covers the textile upper, fortified with a white leather overlay and accented with a crimson Swoosh. A faux fur lining on the interior tongue and collar is reminiscent of Santa’s hat, while the sneaker’s red and green tooling manages to further amplify the yuletide theme.

Jordan B'Loyal PS 'White'
results.story: Fashioned for little kids, the Jordan B’Loyal PS ‘White’ applies a pristine monochrome finish to a retro-inspired mid-top that takes its design cues from legacy Air Jordan models. The sneaker makes use of a white leather upper, fortified with a tonal patent leather overlay that wraps over the toe and across the midfoot. An open-hole tongue combines with a webbing pull tab at the heel to deliver easy on and off. Embroidered Jumpman branding decorates the perforated lateral ankle.

results.name: Renew Lucent GS 'Gunsmoke Violet'
results.story: Built for big kids, the Nike Renew Lucent GS ‘Gunsmoke Violet’ showcases vibrant purple accents on a translucent textile upper in a contrasting dark grey finish. Convenient pull tabs are placed at the tongue and heel, the latter equipped with soft padding for a comfortable fit. A bulky foam midsole delivers plush cushioning with each step. Underfoot, rubber pods in high-wear areas provide durable traction and additional pops of color.

results.name: Nintendo x J.Cole x RS-Dreamer Jr 'Super Mario Sunshine'
results.story: Offered in grade school sizing, the Nintendo x J.Cole x PUMA RS-Dreamer Jr ‘Super Mario Sunshine’ is taken from a capsule collection marking the 35th anniversary of the Super Mario Bros. franchise. A wraparound cord lacing system secures the knit upper, finished in aqua coloring that reflects the tropical waters surrounding Isle Delfino. In an overt nod to the 2002 game, a Shine Sprite graphic decorates the heel overlay, while the Super Mario logo lands on the webbing pull tab atop the tongue.

results.name: Nintendo x J.Cole x RS-Dreamer Little Kid 'Super Mario Sunshine'
results.story: Commemorating the 35th anniversary of the Super Mario Bros. franchise, the Nintendo x J.Cole x PUMA RS-Dreamer Little Kid ‘Super Mario Sunshine’ features a design inspired by the 2002 game set in tropical Isle Delfino. A unique cord lacing system secures the breathable knit upper, rendered in a watery aqua finish and fortified with tonal suede overlays. Unique branding elements include a Shine Sprite graphic on the heel overlay and a Super Mario logo on the webbing pull tab atop the tongue.
